<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="JP">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/To-Label.png" />
    <title>To-Label</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.js"
      integrity="sha256-eKhayi8LEQwp4NKxN+CfCh+3qOVUtJn3QNZ0TciWLP4="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav
      class="navbar bg-dark border-bottom border-bottom-dark navbar-expand-lg fixed-top"
      style="font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold; width: 100%"
      data-bs-theme="dark"
    >
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/" style="font-size: 30px">To-Label</a>
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarTogglerDemo02"
          aria-controls="navbarTogglerDemo02"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
          style="text-align: right"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarTogglerDemo02">
          <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/history">History</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/setting">Setting</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main style="position: absolute; top: 80px; right: 30px; left: 30px">
      <h3
        class="text-center pb-3 pt-3 mt-5 mb-4 border-bottom border-top border-2 text-success-emphasis border-success bg-success-subtle"
      >
        レッテルの結果
      </h3>
      <div class="pb-2 mt-4 border-bottom border-<%= color %> border-5">
        <h4
          class="pb-2 pt-2 px-2 mb-2 border-bottom border-top border-2 text-<%= color %>-emphasis border-<%= color %> bg-<%= color %>-subtle"
          style="text-align: center"
        >
          <%= username %>さんに貼られたレッテル
        </h4>
        <div class="card border-<%= color %> bg-<%= color %>-subtle">
          <div
            class="card-header border-<%= color %> bg-<%= color %>-subtle text-<%= color %>-emphasis"
          >
            <%= username %>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <% your_msg_list.forEach(element =>{%>
            <div
              class="card border-<%= element.color %> bg-<%= element.color %>-subtle text-<%= element.color %>-emphasis"
            >
              <div
                class="card-header border-<%= element.color %> bg-<%= element.color %>-subtle text-<%= element.color %>-emphasis"
              >
                <%= element.from_username %> さんから
              </div>
              <div class="card-body"><%= element.msg %></div>
            </div>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4
        class="pb-2 pt-2 px-2 mb-2 mt-4 border-bottom border-top border-2 text-<%= color %>-emphasis border-<%= color %> bg-<%= color %>-subtle"
        style="text-align: center"
      >
        他の人に貼られたレッテル
      </h4>
      <% for(let i=0; i < other_msg_list.length; i++){ %> <% if(i%2==0){ if(i ==
      other_msg_list.length-1){ %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
          <div
            class="card mb-4 border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle"
          >
            <div
              class="card-header border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle text-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-emphasis"
            >
              <%= other_msg_list[i][0] %> さんに貼られたレッテル
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <% other_msg_list[i][2].forEach(child=>{%>
              <div
                class="card border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
              >
                <div
                  class="card-header border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
                >
                  <%= child.from_username %> さんから
                </div>
                <div class="card-body"><%= child.msg %></div>
              </div>
              <%})%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }else{ %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
          <div
            class="card mb-4 border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle"
          >
            <div
              class="card-header border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle text-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-emphasis"
            >
              <%= other_msg_list[i][0] %> さんに貼られたレッテル
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <% other_msg_list[i][2].forEach(child=>{%>
              <div
                class="card border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
              >
                <div
                  class="card-header border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
                >
                  <%= child.from_username %> さんから
                </div>
                <div class="card-body"><%= child.msg %></div>
              </div>
              <%})%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }}else if(i%2==1){ %>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
          <div
            class="card mb-4 border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle"
          >
            <div
              class="card-header border-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %> bg-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-subtle text-<%= other_msg_list[i][1] %>-emphasis"
            >
              <%= other_msg_list[i][0] %> さんに貼られたレッテル
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <% other_msg_list[i][2].forEach(child=>{%>
              <div
                class="card border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
              >
                <div
                  class="card-header border-<%= child.color %> bg-<%= child.color %>-subtle text-<%= child.color %>-emphasis"
                >
                  <%= child.from_username %> さんから
                </div>
                <div class="card-body"><%= child.msg %></div>
              </div>
              <%})%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }} %>
      <p
        class="px-2 pt-2 pb-2 mt-5 mb-5 bg-danger-subtle border-danger border-top border-bottom border-2 text-danger-emphasis"
        style="text-align: center"
      >
        この部屋は、1日経つと削除されて、アクセスできなくなります。明日以降は、ユーザーのヒストリーページより閲覧ください。
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
